reviewText: Neither disc is good, they are just empty. I will send them back.
Great cross-section of Bob DeNiro's talent. All four films can be converted to uv.

Great collection at an excellent price. ( I've got it for $27). All four movies are very good, no fillers here. The only minor downside I find, is that there is a new extended version of "Once upon a time in America" and if you want it you'll have to purchase it separately
